Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:51.37,title2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur35\t(0,600,\blur0)\fad(0,500)}不　　　　在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:51.37,title3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1000)\fad(300,500)}焦 躁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:51.37,loc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}龍宮島坐標：北緯11°31′37〞 東經145°04′36〞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我要當駕駛員？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 說是確定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是不願意 媽媽就去幫你說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能靠這個去泡妞了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這笨兒子！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公 今天就先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也因為給法芙娜做調整都沒合眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我這當爹的必須要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼需要儘管說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俘虜 吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這種人為什麼能成為神劍型的駕駛員？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會在戰鬥中怯場 被我砍斷手的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你是那部紅色機體的駕駛員？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那部機體歸我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然還能面不改色地戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把我放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這種小丫頭片子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我開門！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的指揮官是誰 馬上把他叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢這麼對我 你們知道會有什麼後果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快給我開門！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:06:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面命令我 不消停點就這麼對付你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 新聯合國那邊聯繫過你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但願一騎他們沒半路碰上祝福者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩結個賬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原稿我存到13號磁盤的資料夾裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 正在確認
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就交到印刷部去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 你最近這麼忙還畫了這麼多頁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是在為夢想戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H827272&\bord0\frz338.2\pos(702,884)}我們是在\N為夢想戰鬥!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是理所當然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這上面寫著一樣的台詞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送你一瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了 大嬸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彙報情況！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4點鐘方向 距離785單位處出現重力反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標 我看看…正以航向740靠近本島
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門發出應答 判斷為質問者型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和以往的不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜以三機陣形展開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:28.29,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(776,1000)}triple dog
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用蝠鱝運輸機搭載機體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.17,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(556,1000)}Devil Ray
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.17,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：蝠鱝 生活在海中 具有翼狀胸鰭的軟骨魚類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們在敵人前進路線上的陸地進行迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不由布倫希爾德系統輔助嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 敵人現在還沒有接近龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前的好像不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20秒之內完成換裝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要裝到蝠鱝運輸機上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移出機架的檢查也別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了 要把孩子們平安無事地帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去跟衛說 那個不適合他啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了也白說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在這方面是頑固透頂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 衛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是男人的初戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小楯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三部法芙娜由蝠鱝運輸機搭載
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在與敵人接觸之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由Mk.Ⅴ帶頭降落 展開三機陣形
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 我的行動代號是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜Mk.Ⅴ 移出機架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝠鱝運輸機 起飛準備就緒 沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們倆沒有做過意識改變狀態測試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能通過協同代碼的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來預測他們的精神是否會發生改變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良的意識在上次出擊時變得極具攻擊性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他兩人應該也會發生變化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,線路暢通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意駕駛員的精神變化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一騎的話 就不會有這種問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝠鱝運輸機 起飛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(Part-b)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩分鐘後將到達目標群島
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各自在射出後4秒之內啟動推進器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移動到預定位置待命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在收到命令之前千萬不要動手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪 在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝠鱝運輸機 前方20公里處出現引力子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去會正面撞上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緊急脫離 切斷吊箱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1重力波防護罩受到攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠程攻擊型的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不玩了 媽媽 我想回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死的祝福者！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來得正好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認法芙娜已落地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各駕駛員的生命體征顯示到屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員的精神狀態果然發生了很大的改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人先主動亮招數了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經確認到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會依據這些情報重新制定戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛 你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 咲良 劍司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說 我有個主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 Mk.Ⅴ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…高帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我故意讓敵人打中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司和咲良就趁這個機會打倒敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事真的能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能打倒敵人 要怎麼做都行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點讓我戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 Mk.Ⅴ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的埃癸斯護盾如果沒能完全防住敵人的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:49.96,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(366,1000)}Aegis
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:49.96,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：埃癸斯 希臘神話中的神盾 相傳宙斯和雅典娜各有一面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大家都會陷入險境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算勝利的幾率是0%
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要相信明天的太陽去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是機動武士！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂七八糟…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則我就把你們全都從駕駛座裡打出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這戰術不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的精神出現了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就當作是衛處在了原本應該由咲良所處的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想一想有什麼能讓裝備埃癸斯護盾的人打頭陣的戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人用的是遠程直線攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅴ應對牠是綽綽有餘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在你要相信駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標正向法芙娜降落地點移動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1重力波防護罩 消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜全機散開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在敵人發動攻擊的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅷ從3點鐘方向開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅲ趁機抄到敵人後方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕大投！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.07,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(746,1000)}smash
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認敵人已被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員都平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良…還好你沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得漂亮 笨兒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在拚命戰鬥 我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公 衛他 衛他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得漂亮啊 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 幹得漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛那小子 幹得漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 在羽佐間你面前這麼高興…真是對不住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請好好誇獎衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼非得進這種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是保護了島吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你們自作主張的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在裡面醒醒腦子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士說得沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛 你還戴著那東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為你射擊太爛了總士才會不滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好反省一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 衛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是 動作再快點 烏龜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…我們怎麼會在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們怎麼都這麼凶啊 好討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說什麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨著協同代碼的形成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個人的精神都會產生顯著的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐間和春日井就有這樣的徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過 沒想到會變化得如此劇烈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:16:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後在出擊時也必須考慮到他們的意識改變狀態才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎為什麼不會發生改變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與法芙娜融為一體所需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是遺傳上的特質與積極的自我否定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是後者極大地影響著駕駛時的意識改變狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的意思是因為一騎平時就一直在否定自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以駕駛法芙娜時心態也不會改變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的精神之所以能維持穩定 是因為你在他的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要穩定的…是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一點一騎也是明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎為什麼出走 你有頭緒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,積極的自我否定前方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:16:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是絕對的肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你和一騎有朝一日能到達那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話說得 就像一騎還在島上一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒指望他會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入夜之前我會放他們三個出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他們的父母也正急著想見自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學會了對對方抱以敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果使彼此漸行漸遠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一點和過去的皆城很像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家那笨兒子這會兒估計已經是人類軍的階下囚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然覺得這樣比駕駛法芙娜戰鬥要好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許我不配做司令啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎那邊還是沒有消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也有可能被祝福者襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者被新聯合國抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是怎樣 都與我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他沒有體諒你？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有試著去體諒他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他我是理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過齊格飛系統
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無數次和他共享過感情 深層心理和戰鬥時的思維
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用機器來窺探人心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這能算得上是理解嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底理解一騎什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少比你理解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是個拖後腿的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在CDC也沒幫上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜也開不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還不止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著大家拚命戰鬥 我竟然還很羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼都不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在沒必要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這句話 為什麼不對一騎也說？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 好久不見 真壁一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房間太小不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要到外面透透氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道生哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 你是第一次出島？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別怨我 這也是規定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快到摩爾多瓦了 在那之前就忍一忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 道生哥你現在住在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有固定的住處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五年前老爸帶我出島以後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就成了人類軍的士兵 到處出任務
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類軍的士兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 能跟我說說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮島的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 我聽說祝福者第一次出現的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:21:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和藏前一起…被同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不該告訴老爸呢 真為難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見弓子…現在怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弓子姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她現在是學校保健室的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她當了老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她以前的夢想是去東京當偶像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,666
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,666？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的代號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待命的時候就別這麼死板了 叫名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的上司
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能叫上司的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個死腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 這傢伙叫卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是砍了你的法芙娜的手的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 剛才她說過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 卡農主動跟人說話還真是少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對一騎很在意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 我們到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新聯合國 人類軍摩爾多瓦基地
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被侵蝕的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.77,0:23:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與過去的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在於未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是新的岔路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 蒼穹的法芙娜 第十三回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.38,0:23:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侵蝕 -祝福者-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡嗎
